snippet.title: Report: Johnny Depp Moves on With 'Made in Chelsea' Star Sophie Hermann After Amber Heard Split
snippet.description:
Report: Johnny Depp Moves on With 'Made in Chelsea' Star Sophie Hermann After Amber Heard Split..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
Amid lengthy legal battle with his ex-wife Amber, the 57-year-old 'Pirates of the Caribbean' actor is reportedly seeing the 33-year-old reality TV star after she hit on him earlier this year.   Sep 4, 2020   AceShowbiz - Johnny Depp may be still entangled with Amber Heard in court, but he doesn't seem to have problems moving on from her romantically. The 57-year-old is reportedly dating German model and "Made in Chelsea" star Sophie Hermann.    According to sources, Johnny and Sophie, who lives in London to film the reality series on which she has appeared since 2013, first came into contact with each other earlier this year.
